bug.short_desc: Only the LAST failed assertion shown in the results pane

long_desc.thetext:
If multiple assertions in a test fail, only the LAST one is shown in the main test results pane. All failed assertions are shown in the log pane though.
S. also the attached screenshot.
We expect either all or the first failing assertion (and not the last one) to be shown in the results pane. Otherwise one would think the preceding assertions have succeeded and would overlook the real error source.
Created attachment 1077 Screenshot of the test runner

The Widget and HTML views now display all exceptions that occurred during a test's execution in the results view.
